high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the sink, then turn right and walk up to the microwave and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the cabinet door above the microwave and pick up the white mug from out of the cabinet, then close the door.
Open the microwave and put the mug inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave back up and remove the now heated mug then close the microwave.
Look back up at the cabinets above the microwave.
Open the upper cabinet above the microwave and put the heated white mug inside, then close the cabinet doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated white mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Grab the cup out of the cabinet.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Place the cup back in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Heat the cup and put it back in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and look at the cabinet above the microwave
Grab the mug out of the cabinet
Heat the mug in the microwave and then take it out
Put the mug in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot mug in a cabinet
